                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=shahar",
                        "name": "shahar",
                        "displayName": "Shahar Evron",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I think I have a patch for this (basically defaulting the 'content-length' header to 0 as suggested) but I need to somehow test this before I commit.\n\nCan you provide some test code reproducing the Nirvanix breakage?\n\nShahar",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=shahar",
                        "name": "shahar",
                        "displayName": "Shahar Evron",
