                        "name": "bruffner",
                        "displayName": "Barry Ruffner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The attached file will let you test the problem.  If the problem is fixed an exception should be raised as follows:\n\nFatal error: Uncaught exception 'Zend_Service_Nirvanix_Exception' with message 'Missing Required Parameter: \nappKey, username, password' in D:\\PHP5\\website\\library\\Zend\\Service\\Nirvanix\\Response.php:119 ",
